                <section class="lq-education-panel lq-next-summary" aria-labelledby="lifeEducationNextTitle">
                    <div class="lq-step-title" id="lifeEducationNextTitle">What happens next?</div>
                    <p class="lq-next-summary-copy">@agentDirectContactName will be in touch shortly to walk you through what may fit and answer any questions you may have. There is no obligation, just a straightforward conversation about your options.</p>
